Text:
Vad e klientutbyte ?

- Jo. bra sula/fart på nedladdningen.
Skyll inte på mig - sa farfar med lösgommen i skinkan.
- I vems skinka låter vi vara osagt.

/Jöteburgare e felstavat

What is so wonderful is that I do have just 75kb upline. 
- And yet, it works to put up such large file.

And I beg your pardon for it.

For those who are so much smarter,they may have an 100/100 line.

- They should not apologize for their state.

/Middle of the forest, since the seventies.
/Pekka Puupää - Närvarandes - Yepp
